data.description: It’s a great day to view this beautiful home, in the great town of Copperas Cove. This beautiful four bedroom two bath brick home is extremely comfortable, and  has plenty of space in a well desired neighborhood. As you enter you will love the large foyer! The large living room features trendy wood- look tiles, large stone wood burning fireplace, and High ceiling. Off the living room is a large formal dining that could also be used as an office space. The kitchen has real wood cabinets, granite counters, and a spacious island along with another dining nook. The main bedroom is on one side of the home for maximum privacy.  It features a walk-in closet , garden bathtub with a separate shower, very large vanity with double sinks, and granite counter. On the other side of the home, you will find three more great size bedrooms with new trendy wallpaper,  and a full bathroom. Enjoy the covered patio all year long with a view of  beautiful mature trees!
